snippet.title: Introducing Project Rap Rabbit
snippet.description:
Introducing Project Rap Rabbit, the new rhythm-action adventure from Masaya Matsuura (PaRappa The Rapper, Vib-Ribbon) and Keiichi Yano (Gitaroo Man, Osu! Tatakae! Ouendan). 
For daily updates, follow us on Twitter - @ProRapRabbit - and like us on Facebook: www.facebook.com/projectraprabbit.
